《'''Fly Me to the Moon'''》通常被譯為“帶我飛向月球”{{refnest|group="注释"|译名参考自搜狐网。<ref>{{cite web|author=董文|title=22首西城男孩经典情歌 随时欢唱的真爱时光(图)|url=http://music.yule.sohu.com/20090324/n262970372.shtml|publisher=搜狐网|accessdate=2014-06-30|date=2009-03-24|quote=7 Fly Me To The Moon(带我飞向月球)|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714142126/http://music.yule.sohu.com/20090324/n262970372.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}，原名《In Other Words》（换句话说），原是由{{le|巴特·霍华德|Bart Howard}}写于1954年的一首[[华尔兹|华尔兹]]舞曲<ref name="易车网"/>。{{le|凯·巴拉德|Kaye Ballard}}在1954年第一次录制了这首歌曲。从那时起，它开始成为一首多次被翻唱的[[爵士经典曲|爵士经典曲]]。[[法蘭·仙納杜拉|法蘭·仙納杜拉]]的1964年录制版本与[[阿波罗登月计划|阿波罗登月计划]]密切相关。

== 歌曲的创作和早期公演 ==
1954年创作这首后来以《带我飞向月球》之名而著称的歌曲时，巴特·霍华德已经投身音乐创作超过20年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://data.desmoinesregister.com/dmr/famous-iowans/bart-howard |title=Famous Iowans - Bart Howard | The Des Moines Register | DesMoinesRegister.com |publisher=Data.desmoinesregister.com |date= |accessdate=2013-12-07 |language=en |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131207062000/http://data.desmoinesregister.com/dmr/famous-iowans/bart-howard |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他为[[卡巴萊|卡巴萊]]歌手弹钢琴伴奏，也同他的偶像[[科尔·波特|科尔·波特]]{{refn|group="注释"|美国作词家、作曲家，译名参考自新浪网。<ref>{{cite web|author=zjy|title=那些深受精神疾病折磨的作家和艺术家|url=http://book.sina.com.cn/newsyc/a/2013-04-18/1135454057.shtml|publisher=新浪网|accessdate=2014-07-05|language=zh-cn|date=2013-04-18|quote=科尔·波特(Cole Porter)，美国词作家和曲作家|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714231504/http://book.sina.com.cn/newsyc/a/2013-04-18/1135454057.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}一起写歌<ref name="nytimes2004">{{cite news |author=By STEPHEN HOLDENPublished: February 23, 2004 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/02/23/arts/bart-howard-88-songwriter-known-for-fly-me-to-the-moon.html |title=Bart Howard, 88, Songwriter Known for 'Fly Me to the Moon' - New York Times |publisher=Nytimes.com |date=2004-02-23 |accessdate=2013-12-07 |language=en |archive-date=2013-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219204841/http://www.nytimes.com//2004/02/23/arts/bart-howard-88-songwriter-known-for-fly-me-to-the-moon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。应发行商的发行单曲的要求<ref>James Gavin, "Intimate Nights: The Golden age Of New York Cabaret", New York, Back Stage Books, 2006 cited in http://greatamericansongbook.net/pages/songs/f/fly_me_to_the_moon.html {{Wayback|url=http://greatamericansongbook.net/pages/songs/f/fly_me_to_the_moon.html |date=20160818092042 }}, Retrieved 26 November 2013</ref>，巴特·霍华德以华尔兹曲调写了首卡巴萊民谣<ref name="autogenerated411">Will Friedwald, "Sinatra! The Song Is You: A Singer's Art", Scribner, New York, 1995, page 411</ref>名为《In Other Words》。发行商试图让他将歌词由“fly me to the moon”改成“take me to the moon”，但霍华德拒绝了<ref name="nytimes1988">Stephen Holden, "Product of 20 Minutes: A Million Dollar Song", New York Times, Published December 19, 1988 http://www.nytimes.com/1988/12/19/arts/product-of-20-minutes-a-million-dollar-song.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1988/12/19/arts/product-of-20-minutes-a-million-dollar-song.html |date=20131219212335 }}, Retrieved 26 November 2013</ref>。 幾年之後他回憶道：「我花了20年才知道要怎麼在20分鐘內寫出一首歌」。（“... it took me 20 years to find out how to write a song in 20 minutes".<ref name="nytimes1988"/>）
最初這首歌是1954年由Kaye Ballard錄音，當時是以「In Other Words」之名推出。後來Portia Nelson也翻唱了這首歌，而「Fly Me to the Moon」這個名字則是Johnny Mathis在1956年推出專輯之時出現的<ref>{{cite news|title=第一首在月亮上播放的人类歌曲|url=http://news.qq.com/a/20071011/004270.htm|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=腾讯网|date=2007-10-11|language=zh-cn|quote=是首华尔兹舞曲……一位出版商建议将其改名为"Take Me to the Moon"……这首歌定名为我们今天看到的"Fly Me to the Moon"……佩姬·李1960年演唱的版本成名……这首歌被写成"Fly Me to the Moon(In Other Words)"……多丽丝·黛、朱迪·贾 兰等好莱坞女星演唱……通过阿波罗飞船送上月球……第一首在月球上播放的人类歌曲|archive-date=2019-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016183312/https://www.qq.com/?froma|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

現在最為人所知的版本是1964年由Quincy Jones編曲，由[[法蘭·仙納杜拉|法蘭·仙納杜拉]]演唱並收錄於《It Might as Well Be Swing》這張專輯中的版本。此時美國正推行[[阿波羅10號|阿波羅10號]]的登月計畫，故這首歌推出之後大受歡迎，甚至成為此年代的代表曲。其受歡迎程度之甚，1969年[[阿波羅11號|阿波羅11號]]登陸月球時艙中也播放著本曲。

==《In Other Words》早期的录音==
{{le|凯·巴拉德|Kaye Ballard}}《In Other Words》的第一支商业发售的录音<ref>{{cite web |title=Kaye Ballard, "In Other Words", Decca, 9-29114, 1954 |url=http://www.discogs.com/Kaye-Ballard-In-Other-Words-Lazy-Afternoon/release/4935944 |accessdate=26 November 2013 |language=en |archive-date=2015-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612070525/http://www.discogs.com/Kaye-Ballard-In-Other-Words-Lazy-Afternoon/release/4935944 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这张唱片1954年4月由迪卡发布<ref>45cat, Decca, 9-29114,http://www.45cat.com/record/929114 {{Wayback|url=http://www.45cat.com/record/929114 |date=20141213023516 }}, Retrieved 27 November 2013</ref>。2010年在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上被上传的一段凯·巴拉德录制《In Other Words》的影片有超过80,000的点击量<ref>YouTube, In Other Words (original) - Kaye Ballard 1954, Uploaded 14 May 2010:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcwlGjDNkkw {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcwlGjDNkkw |date=20141027220049 }}, Retrieved 16 April 2014</ref>。1954年5月8日《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》上刊登的一则简单介绍讲道《In Other Words》是“一首唱出了巴拉德小姐的感觉的情歌”<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=YB8EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA24&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Nielsen Business Media, Inc., ''Billboard'',|date=1954-05-08|page=24|accessdate=15 April 2014|journal=|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417023755/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=YB8EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA24&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在接下来的几年里，许多的[[爵士乐|爵士乐]]和[[卡巴萊|卡巴萊]]歌手陆续以[[迷你專輯|EP]]或者[[密紋唱片|LP录音]][[音樂專輯|专辑]]的形式发布了《In Other Words》这首歌的[[翻唱|翻唱]]版本，这其中包括了{{le|克里斯·康纳|Chris Connor}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Chris Connor - Chris (Vinyl, LP)|url=http://www.discogs.com/Chris-Connor-Chris/release/805394|publisher=Discogs|accessdate=2014-07-05|language=en|quote=B6 In Other Words……|archive-date=2013-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211233238/http://www.discogs.com/Chris-Connor-Chris/release/805394|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{le|约翰尼·马蒂斯|Johnny Mathis}}<ref>Johnny Mathis, "Johnny Mathis", Columbia CL 887,1956 http://www.discogs.com/Johnny-Mathis-Johnny-Mathis/master/543310 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Johnny-Mathis-Johnny-Mathis/master/543310 |date=20141225033322 }}, Retrieved 26 November 2013</ref>{{refn|group="注释"|美国黑人歌手，译名参考自光明网。<ref>{{cite web|title=金润吉有绝对优势走更远|url=http://news.gmw.cn/newspaper/2013-09/08/content_2082686.htm|publisher=光明网|accessdate=2014-07-05|language=zh-cn|date=2013-09-08|quote=美国黑人歌手Johnny Mathis（约翰尼·马蒂斯）|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715014650/http://news.gmw.cn/newspaper/2013-09/08/content_2082686.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}、[[Portia_Nelson|Portia Nelson]]<ref>Portia Nelson, "Let Me Love You: Portia Nelson Sings the Songs of Bart Howard", New Sound (NS)3002, 1956,  http://www.discogs.com/Portia-Nelson-Bart-Howard-Let-Me-Love-You/release/5592051 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Portia-Nelson-Bart-Howard-Let-Me-Love-You/release/5592051 |date=20161019102123 }}, Retrieved 16 April 2014</ref>以及[[南希·威尔森|南希·威尔森]]<ref>Nancy Wilson, "Like in Love", Capitol Records, T-1319/ST-1319, 1960 http://www.discogs.com/Nancy-Wilson-Like-In-Love/master/543319 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Nancy-Wilson-Like-In-Love/master/543319 |date=20150222133931 }}, Retrieved 27 November 2013</ref>{{refn|group="注释"|译名参考自腾讯网。<ref>{{cite web|author=celiawu|title=图文：南希-威尔森获得最佳爵士演唱专辑奖|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20070212/000352.htm|accessdate=2014-07-05|language=zh-cn|date=2007-02-12|quote=南希·威尔森（Nancy Wilson）凭借专辑《Tur……|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714230303/http://ent.qq.com/a/20070212/000352.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}等。{{le|埃迪·戈梅|Eydie Gormé}}{{refn|group="注释"|美国女歌手，曾获得格莱美奖，译名参考自搜狐娱乐。<ref>{{cite news|author=王钲|title=格莱美传奇女歌手埃迪-戈梅去世 享年84岁|url=http://yule.sohu.com/20130812/n383955105.shtml|accessdate=2014-07-05|newspaper=搜狐娱乐|date=2013-08-12|language=zh-cn|quote=美国传奇女歌手……曾获得格莱美奖的埃迪·戈梅（Eydie Gorme）不幸逝世|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714212718/http://yule.sohu.com/20130812/n383955105.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}1958年在她的专辑《Eydie In Love》中翻唱了这首歌曲<ref>"Eydie In Love", ABC Paramount ABC/ABCS 246, 1958 as detailed in David Edwards, Patrice Eyries, and Mike Callahan, "ABC-Paramount Album Discography, Part 2 ABC-200 to 299 (1957-1959)", http://www.bsnpubs.com/abc/abc200.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.bsnpubs.com/abc/abc200.html |date=20161016193822 }}, Retrieved 26 November 2013</ref>，并获得了[[Cashbox_(magazine)|Cashbox]]专辑排行榜第20名<ref>Cashbox Charts, Week of 18 October 1958, http://hitsofalldecades.com/chart_hits/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1887&Itemid=52 {{Wayback|url=http://hitsofalldecades.com/chart_hits/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1887&Itemid=52 |date=20180919161424 }}, Retrieved 1 December 2013</ref>以及[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]提名<ref>"Grammy Award for Best Female Pop Vocal Performance", https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grammy_Award_for_Best_Female_Pop_Vocal_Performance {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grammy_Award_for_Best_Female_Pop_Vocal_Performance |date=20140714053754 }}, Retrieved 14 April 2014</ref>
