1960年[[佩姬·李|佩姬·李]]{{refn|group="注释"|name="易车网"}}录制了这首歌<ref>{{citeweb|title=Peggy Lee, "Pretty Eyes",Capitol T 1401 /ST 1401, 1960|url=http://www.discogs.com/Peggy-Lee-Pretty-Eyes/master/360670|accessdate=26 November 2013|language=en|archive-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306071046/http://www.discogs.com/Peggy-Lee-Pretty-Eyes/master/360670|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而当在《{{le|艾德·苏利文秀|The Ed Sullivan Show}}》{{refn|group="注释"|美国一档电视节目，二十世纪五十年代曾有高达50%的[[收视率|收视率]]，[[猫王|猫王]]就是凭借在这个节目中的表演而出名，译名参考自新浪网<ref>{{cite web|author=yxj|title=McGuire姐妹合唱团成员去世 享年84岁|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2012-09-11/10193737939.shtml|publisher=新浪网|accessdate=2014-07-06|language=zh-cn|date=2012-09-11|quote=电视节目“艾德-苏利文秀”(The Ed Sullivan Show)上……猫王就是在这个节目中一炮而红|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714183156/http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2012-09-11/10193737939.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，部分来源翻译成《艾德苏利文剧场》<ref>{{cite web|author=DinK|title=传统媒体的逆袭：电视行业为何迎来黄金时代？|url=http://www.199it.com/archives/109128.html|publisher=199IT|accessdate=2014-07-06|language=zh-cn|date=2013-05-04|quote=电视综艺节目“艾德苏利文剧场”（The Ed Sullivan Show）|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714145614/http://www.199it.com/archives/109128.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}上当众表演后，则让这首歌一炮而红<ref name="nytimes2004"/>。当歌曲的知名度上升后，这首歌被更多地传称为《Fly Me To The Moon》<ref>Todd S. Jenkins, "Bart Howard: Composer of 'Fly Me To The Moon', 'Let Me Love You' ", http://www.jazzhouse.org/gone/lastpost2.php3?edit=1078245748 {{Wayback|url=http://www.jazzhouse.org/gone/lastpost2.php3?edit=1078245748 |date=20181204010131 }}, Retrieved 26 November 2013</ref>。而在1963年，佩吉·李说服巴特·霍华德正式将歌名改为《Fly Me To The Moon》<ref name="nytimes1988"/>。在20世纪60年代早期，这首歌以新歌名被许多歌手所传唱，如[[納·京·高爾|納·京·高爾]]<ref>Nat King Cole and George Shearing, Nat King Cole Sings George Shearing Plays, Capitol Records SM-1675, 1962, http://www.discogs.com/Nat-King-Cole-George-Shearing-Nat-King-Cole-Sings-George-Shearing-Plays/release/2656427 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Nat-King-Cole-George-Shearing-Nat-King-Cole-Sings-George-Shearing-Plays/release/2656427 |date=20120813053407 }}, Retrieved 1 December 2013</ref>、[[莎拉·沃恩|莎拉·沃恩]]<ref>Sarah Vaughan, "You're Mine You", Roulette Records, SR 52082, 1962, http://www.discogs.com/Sarah-Vaughan-Youre-Mine-You/release/3178058 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Sarah-Vaughan-Youre-Mine-You/release/3178058 |date=20160308200106 }}, Retrieved 1 December 2013</ref>和{{le|布兰达·李|Brenda Lee}}<ref>Brenda Lee, "All Alone Am I", Decca DL 74370 , 1963, http://www.discogs.com/Brenda-Lee-All-Alone-Am-I/release/3036469 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Brenda-Lee-All-Alone-Am-I/release/3036469 |date=20150926083427 }}, Retrieved 1 December 2013</ref>{{refn|group="注释"|美国乡村音乐歌手，译名参考自腾讯网。<ref>{{cite web|author=洋娃娃|title=Four Tops、Brenda Lee获51届格莱美终身成就奖|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20081225/000222.htm|publisher=腾讯网|accessdate=2014-07-06|language=zh-cn|date=2008-12-25|quote=乡村音乐歌手布兰达·李(Brenda Lee)|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714202849/http://ent.qq.com/a/20081225/000222.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}。{{le|科尼·弗朗西斯|Connie Francis}}{{refn|group="注释"|五六十年代流行乐歌手，译名参考自新浪网。<ref>{{cite web|author=龙龙|title=老牌歌手科尼-弗朗西斯住院 错过纽约演出(图)|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2008-07-26/12332115348.shtml|publisher=新浪网|accessdate=2014-07-06|language=zh-cn|date=2008-07-26|quote=歌手科尼-弗朗西斯(Connie Francis(听歌))……五六十年代时风靡整个流行乐坛|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714223524/http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2008-07-26/12332115348.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}于1963年发行了这首歌的两支非英语版本：[[意大利语|意大利语]]版的《Portami Con Te》<ref>45cat, MGM K 2078, 1963 http://www.45cat.com/record/k2078 {{Wayback|url=http://www.45cat.com/record/k2078 |date=20131211075417 }}</ref>和[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]版的《Llévame A La Luna》<ref>45cat, MGM, HT 057-78, 1963,http://www.45cat.com/record/ht05778 {{Wayback|url=http://www.45cat.com/record/ht05778 |date=20131211075258 }}</ref>。

1962年[[Joe_Harnell|Joe Harnell]]改编并录制的[[巴薩諾瓦|巴薩諾瓦]]风格的器乐版本并于当年年底作为单曲发行<ref>Joe Harnell & His Orchestra, "Fly Me To The Moon", Kapp Records K-497X, http://www.discogs.com/Joe-Harnell-And-His-Orchestra-Fly-Me-To-The-Moon-Harlem-Nocturne/master/278847 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Joe-Harnell-And-His-Orchestra-Fly-Me-To-The-Moon-Harlem-Nocturne/master/278847 |date=20150310041743 }}</ref>。这首歌1963年在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]排名第14位<ref>[http://books.google.com.au/books?id=dgsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA51&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=hot%201oo%20harnell%2028&f=false Nielsen Business Media, Inc., ''Billboard'', 23 February 1963, Page 28] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=dgsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA51&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=hot%201oo%20harnell%2028&f=false |date=20140323172734 }}, Retrieved 15 April 2014</ref>并帮助获得格莱美奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2005/jul/17/local/me-harnell17 |title=Joe Harnell, 80; Pianist, Conductor, Composer, Arranger - Los Angeles Times |publisher=Articles.latimes.com |date=1994-09-29 |accessdate=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218082414/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/jul/17/local/me-harnell17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Harnell录制的版本同时也收录于他的专辑《Fly Me To The Moon And The Bossa Nova Pops》中于1963年初发行<ref>Joe Harnell His Piano and Orchestra, "Fly Me to the Moon Bossa Nova Pops", http://www.discogs.com/Joe-Harnell-His-Piano-And-Orchestra-Fly-Me-To-The-Moon-And-The-Bossa-Nova-Pops/master/231087 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Joe-Harnell-His-Piano-And-Orchestra-Fly-Me-To-The-Moon-And-The-Bossa-Nova-Pops/master/231087 |date=20150612080643 }}, Retrieved 29 November 20132</ref>并在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]上排名第3位<ref>[http://books.google.com.au/books?id=eQsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=66&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=harnell%2050%20150%20stereo%20monaural&f=false Nielsen Business Media, Inc., ''Billboard'', 16 March 1963, Page 66] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=eQsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=66&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=harnell%2050%20150%20stereo%20monaural&f=false |date=20140417034257 }}, Retrieved 15 April 2014</ref>。20世纪60年代，许多歌手，如{{le|罗伊·海恩斯|Roy Haynes}}<ref>Roy Haynes Quartet, "Out in the Afternoon", http://www.discogs.com/Roy-Haynes-Quartet-Out-Of-The-Afternoon/master/266318 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Roy-Haynes-Quartet-Out-Of-The-Afternoon/master/266318 |date=20150609220023 }}, Retrieved 30 November 2013</ref>{{refn|group="注释"|美国爵士音乐家，译名参考自新浪网。<ref>{{cite web|title=多莉·帕顿获颁格莱美终身成就奖|url=http://sh.sina.com.cn/news/2010-12-30/0112167672.html|publisher=新浪网|accessdate=2014-07-07|date=2010-12-30|quote=爵士音乐家罗伊·海恩斯（Roy Haynes）|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714215333/http://sh.sina.com.cn/news/2010-12-30/0112167672.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}、[[Al_Hirt|Al Hirt]]<ref>Al Hirt, "Honey in the Horn", RCA Victor, LPM 2763, 1963, http://www.discogs.com/Al-Hirt-Honey-In-The-Horn/release/1336377 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Al-Hirt-Honey-In-The-Horn/release/1336377 |date=20141118015612 }}, Retrieved 14 April 2014</ref>和{{le|奥斯卡·彼得森|Oscar Peterson}}<ref>The Oscar Peterson Trio, ''The Oscar Peterson Trio Plays'', Verve Records, V-8591 and VS-8591, 1964: http://www.discogs.com/Oscar-Peterson-Trio-The-Oscar-Peterson-Trio-Plays/master/414161 {{Wayback|url=http://www.discogs.com/Oscar-Peterson-Trio-The-Oscar-Peterson-Trio-Plays/master/414161 |date=20150612073608 }}, Retrieved 15 April 2014</ref>{{refn|group="注释"|美国爵士音乐家，译名参考自新浪网。<ref>{{cite web|title=加拿大感恩节推选十大最具代表性乐队艺人(图)|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2010-10-11/10403108541.shtml|publisher=新浪网|accessdate=2014-07-07|date=2010-12-30|quote=奥斯卡·彼得森(Oscar Peterson，1925-2007)……出生在魁北克的彼得森被爵士大师艾灵顿公爵称为“琴键王公”|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714230101/http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2010-10-11/10403108541.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}等都曾翻唱过这首歌。

==被确认为“标志性歌曲”==
1999年，美国{{le|歌曲创作名人堂|Songwriters Hall of Fame}} 将“Fly Me to the Moon”确立为“标志性歌曲”，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.songwritershalloffame.org/ceremony/C3111 |title=1999 Award and Induction Ceremony |publisher=Songwriters Hall of Fame |date=1999-06-09 |accessdate=2013-12-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207000556/http://songwritershalloffame.org/ceremony/C3111 |archivedate=2013-12-07 }}</ref> 这是用来奖励“……每年最具代表性的歌曲，从而来肯定其对于人类文化历史上的独特贡献。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.songwritershalloffame.org/ceremony/awards/C3006 |title=Towering Song |publisher=Songwriters Hall of Fame |date= |accessdate=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207005202/http://songwritershalloffame.org/ceremony/awards/C3006 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
